OL,3,CNI MPs call for rethink of
OL,4,Cagricultural inheritance tax
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's MPs and peers have
OL,7,Funited in a plea to the Government to
OL,8,Frethink planned changes to inheritance
OL,9,Ftax for farmers.
OL,11,FIn a letter to Chancellor Rachel
OL,12,FReeves, DUP MP Carla Lockhart warned
OL,13,Fit could threaten the generational
OL,14,Ftransfer of farms, disrupt rural
OL,15,Fcommunities and undermine the long-
OL,16,Fterm security of the agricultural
OL,17,Fsector.
