OL,6,FThe Stormont Department of
OL,7,FAgriculture, Environment and Rural
OL,8,FAffairs has estimated that around a
OL,9,Fthird of farms in Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fwill be affected.
OL,12,FIt comes as farmers plan to take part
OL,13,Fin an Ulster Farmers' Union rally in
OL,14,FLisburn, Co Antrim, on Monday evening.
OL,16,FA large-scale protest is expected to
OL,17,Ftake place at Whitehall on Tuesday.
