OL,3,CNI MPs call for rethink of
OL,4,Cagricultural inheritance tax
OL,6,FMs Lockhart has urged the Chancellor
OL,7,Fto reconsider her plans to axe
OL,8,Fhistoric agricultural property relief
OL,9,F(APR) on inheritance tax announced in
OL,10,Fthe recent Budget.
OL,12,FFrom April 2026, APR will only apply
OL,13,Fto the first #1 million of the estate,
OL,14,Fwith anything over that value taxed at
OL,15,F20%.
