OL,3,CNI MPs call for rethink of
OL,4,Cagricultural inheritance tax
OL,6,FThe letter, which was circulated to
OL,7,Fthe Treasury, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer and Defra minister Daniel
OL,9,FZeichner, has been countersigned by
OL,10,Fall sitting Northern Ireland MPs and
OL,11,Fmembers of the House of Lords.
OL,13,FMs Lockhart described a "strong united
OL,14,Fmessage on this issue".
OL,16,F"Agriculture isn't just a cornerstone
OL,17,Fof Northern Ireland's economy, it is a
OL,18,Ffundamental part of local communities
OL,19,Fand rural life," she said.
