OL,3,CNI MPs call for rethink of
OL,4,Cagricultural inheritance tax
OL,6,F"With more than 26,000 farms, the agri-
OL,7,Ffood sector supports tens of thousands
OL,8,Fof families across the region,
OL,9,Fproviding vital economic, social and
OL,10,Fcultural contributions.
OL,12,F"The removal of Agricultural Property
OL,13,FRelief will place a substantial and
OL,14,Funfair financial burden on family
OL,15,Ffarms, jeopardise their ability to
OL,16,Fpass on these assets to future
OL,17,Fgenerations and risk the
OL,18,Fsustainability of family-owned farming
OL,19,Foperations."
