OL,4,Cagricultural inheritance tax
OL,6,FMs Lockhart said the plan risks
OL,7,Fexacerbating existing pressures
OL,8,Falready faced by the agricultural
OL,9,Fsector, including rising operational
OL,10,Fcosts, challenges from changing trade
OL,11,Fconditions and the uncertainties
OL,12,Fassociated with climate policies.
OL,14,FShe said at least a third of all farms
OL,15,Fin Northern Ireland are set to be
OL,16,Faffected, and 75% of dairy farms.
