OL,6,F"Whilst almost #14,000 per acre is
OL,7,Freported as the average price, land
OL,8,Fvalues in Northern Ireland vary
OL,9,Fmassively, depending on location and
OL,10,Fsector, but are in the main more
OL,11,Fexpensive than elsewhere in the United
OL,12,FKingdom," Ms Lockhart wrote in her
OL,13,Fletter to the Chancellor.
