OL,3,CNI MPs call for rethink of
OL,4,Cagricultural inheritance tax
OL,6,F"Unlike other types of businesses,
OL,7,Ffarming is asset-rich but often cash-
OL,8,Fpoor, making inheritance tax
OL,9,Fliabilities particularly difficult to
OL,10,Fmeet without significant
OL,11,Frestructuring, borrowing, or asset
OL,12,Fdisposal, potentially leading to
OL,13,Ffragmentation or loss of productive
OL,14,Fland.
