OL,3,CNI MPs call for rethink of
OL,4,Cagricultural inheritance tax
OL,6,F"We recognise and support the need for
OL,7,Fa fair tax system, but we strongly
OL,8,Fbelieve that removing APR will
OL,9,Finadvertently threaten the
OL,10,Fgenerational transfer of farms,
OL,11,Fdisrupt rural communities and
OL,12,Fundermine the long-term security of
OL,13,Four agricultural sector.
OL,15,F"We strongly urge the government to
OL,16,Freconsider this decision and to
OL,17,Fpreserve APR for agricultural
OL,18,Fproperties to ensure that the next
OL,19,Fgeneration can continue to work and
OL,20,Fthrive in this essential industry.
